item.title: Updated CV
item.description: Heyo! I am finally doing a blog post again - was able to update the site with my newest publications, several new packages, and presentations. Check out the research presentation page for updates on presentations given this year, including several workshops (with provided code). Packages: Buchanan, E. M. (2024). visualizemi: Visualization, Effect Size, and Replication of Measurement Invariance for Registered Reports. R package version 0.0.1. https://github.com/doomlab/visualizemi Buchanan, E. M. (2024). Visualizing Sensitivity.
